name: The Austin Chair
description: The understated luxury of the popular Austin dining chair makes it the perfect choice for both intimate dining and elegant entertaining. The legs are finished in a dark-tinted beech, a rich but refined look that contrasts pleasingly with delicate upholstery. The tub-shaped design ensures optimum comfort and support, while the splayed back legs complement the gentle curves of the backrest in a smart seating solution. As with other DAVIDSON chairs, the Austin can be upholstered in a range of fabrics or leathers to suit your interior.
